WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:05.566
My dear concubine is in high spirits.

2
00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:08.066
This humble servant greets His Majesty.

3
00:00:08.066 --> 00:00:09.400
What brings His Majesty here?

4
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:10.566
If I don't come,

5
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:12.833
are you afraid you might lose favor?

6
00:00:13.900 --> 00:00:15.866
Your Majesty, you misunderstand.

7
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.666
These are famous troupes from the capital.

8
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:20.833
They are called the "Capital's Aifosi."

9
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:23.866
They only perform.

10
00:00:24.366 --> 00:00:25.966
They don't sell themselves or make a fuss.

11
00:00:25.966 --> 00:00:27.466
Get them all out!

12
00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:35.366
You can come back.

13
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.233
During this time,

14
00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:43.166
why haven’t you visited me?

15
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:45.666
Your Majesty, you are still injured.

16
00:00:45.666 --> 00:00:46.700
You need to rest.

17
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.300
I didn’t dare disturb you.

18
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:52.300
Does he still resent me for that day?

19
00:00:52.666 --> 00:00:54.866
Have I made him feel insecure?

20
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:56.400
That day was not about breaking a promise.

21
00:00:56.500 --> 00:00:58.166
It was just to deal with some matters.

22
00:01:02.966 --> 00:01:04.900
I will never let go of your hand again.

23
00:01:04.900 --> 00:01:07.900
If I ever make you unhappy in the future,

24
00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:09.200
just tell me directly.

25
00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.566
I will definitely change.

26
00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:14.866
Hmph, you suddenly changed so much, treating me so well.

27
00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:17.766
This is what Your Majesty said.

28
00:01:19.700 --> 00:01:21.100
If it weren’t for you,

29
00:01:21.266 --> 00:01:22.666
I’d be outside the palace now,

30
00:01:22.666 --> 00:01:24.433
seeing a wider world.

31
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.600
What did I do wrong again?

32
00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:29.066
Ah.

33
00:01:29.566 --> 00:01:31.966
When you entered just now, did you step with your right foot?

34
00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.100
I’m not happy.

35
00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:36.833
Ah.
